text:
A few weeks ago, much of the Ethereum community came together in South America as we reunited for Devcon VI in Bogotá. 

Today, we want thank everyone that participated, and to share highlights, media, and to recap the fun. 

Read our recap here(!): https://t.co/q0il18n9xs

👇👇👇

(This is separate from the POAP you will receive after completing the Devcon survey. You can find the survey in your emails) https://t.co/pAXY7QqPl8

‼️Devcon attendees!

Check your email and be eligible for a POAP:

We would love to hear your feedback on Devcon VI. Fill out the survey before the deadline (30 Nov) and receive a POAP!

Don't forget to check your spam folder!
